    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not really a choice i can make, honestly. the publisher basically said it's part of the contract for the new books. if i don't switch you over to the safety template, they won't release the next installment. it's just how they want to manage the brand now. why do you think it's such a big deal if we just stick to the safer, more standard stuff?",
